The tokenizer implementation in this directory, the embedded dictionary
(`dict_le.dat.zst`), and the embedded HMM model (`jieba_hmm_model.dat`) are
derived from the cppjieba project by Yanyi Wu:

    https://github.com/yanyiwu/cppjieba

The dictionary and model inputs are generated from the upstream
`dict/jieba.dict.utf8` and HMM probability tables (see `generate_dict.py` and
`generate_hmm_model.py` for the reproduction procedure). cppjieba is
distributed under the MIT License, reproduced verbatim below.

